# Hyperloop AI — Partner Program

**The Referral Partner Program**
A lifetime commission arrangement for trusted connections who introduce Hyperloop AI to business owners in their network. Simple, transparent, and built to reward long-term relationships.

---

## The deal
**10% Commission**
Flat 10% on every dollar your referred client pays Hyperloop AI. Retainer months, project fees, expansions — all of it. For as long as that client stays. No expiry, no tiers, no fine print.

### What that looks like in practice
- Project client($15K one-off project): $1500 Paid once on completion
- Retainer client($5K/month retainer): $500/mo Every month they're active
- Retainer × 12 months($5K/month, full year): $6,000 From a single introduction

---

## How it works
### Step 01
You make the introduction
Connect us with a business owner in your network — via email, WhatsApp, LinkedIn, or setup a Google Meet/Zoom. We take it from there.

### Step 02
We close and deliver
We handle all sales, scoping, and delivery. You don't need to sell anything — just make the intro and we do the rest.

### Step 03
You get paid
Once the client pays their first invoice, your commission is calculated and sent. For retainers, you receive your 10% every month alongside their payment cycle.

---

## Terms at a glance
- Commission applies to all revenue from your referred client — retainers, projects, and any upsells
- Lifetime means lifetime — commissions continue for the full duration of the client relationship, no cap
- Referral is tracked from first introduction — documented in writing so there's never ambiguity
- Payouts are processed within 7 days of receiving the client's payment
- No minimum referrals required — one introduction is enough to be in the program
- You can refer multiple clients — commissions stack independently per client. If you refer 3 clients on retainers, you're earning $1,500/month passively.

